net.sf.mmm.util.value.api

Interface StringValueConverter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GenericValueConverter<String>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StringValueConverterImpl

    @ComponentSpecification
public interface StringValueConverter
extends GenericValueConverter<String>
    This is a sub-interface of GenericValueConverter for the most common value type String. It is typically used for dealing with values (e.g. when reading configurations).
    Since:
    1.0.2
    Author:
